== Death ==
On May 10, 2781, Roosevelt died of old age.

== Relationships and children ==
From 2678 to 2679, Roosevelt dated a student named Steve Brown (2659-2741). They had a daughter, Venus Roosevelt XII (2679-2765), from their first relationship.

From 2687 to 2688, Roosevelt and Brown dated again. They had a son, Carlton Roosevelt XVIII (2688-2767), from their second relationship.

From 2717 to 2719, Roosevelt and Brown dated a third time. They had a son, August Roosevelt (2719-after 2784), from their third relationship.

From 2748 to 2751, Roosevelt dated her talent agent, Angel Hole (2668-2758). They had two children, Penelope Hole (2750-after 2784) and [[Boomer Roosevelt]].

In 2780, Roosevelt started dating her talent agent, Charles Roosevelt (2742-after 2781).

